headline: CoStar Group Acquires Ag-Analytics, Augmenting Land.com Services and Capabilities
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., February 14, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP) ("CoStar Group," "we" or "our"), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information and analytics in the commercial and residential property markets, today announced that it has acquired agricultural data company Ag-Analytics.
